Welcome to Willpak Industries Inc.

Manufacturer of Astra/Hammond Automotive Accessories and the Touchless Car Cover

We offer a broad line of Astra/Hammond-branded car, truck and van accessories, including our premier Aluminum and ABS Rear Window Louvers, going back to the mid 60s. We also manufacture many other complimentary accessories like Side Window Louvers, Side Window Scoops, Hood Scoops, Chin Spoilers, Rear Quarter Scoops, Tire Covers and now, the Touchless Car Cover. Our tooling is produced with precision and careful craftsmanship to the exacting standards demanded by our customers. Willpak’s ongoing commitment to manufacturing and product excellence has allowed us to enjoy an exceptionally strong reputation throughout the automotive aftermarket industry.

Mission Statement

Our mission is simple; offer a broad range of complementing thermoformed and automotive products that have leading designs and high quality and to continually develop new products  for manufacture and distribution.
